Dear colleague,

You find enclosed the first announcement of MCO'08

Modelling, Computation and Optimization
in Information Systems and Management Sciences (MCO'08)
September 8-10, 2008, Metz, France http://lita.sciences.univ-metz.fr/~mco08/

and its flyer for advertising.

The refereed Proceedings of MCO'08 will include all papers accepted for the conference and will be
published in a Lecture Notes series of Springer. Authors of accepted papers are invited to submit a longer
version of their work to be published in two Special Issues of International Journals : Computational and
Management Science and Computational Optimization and Applications.

We are pleased to invite you to attend the conference and to deliver/organize a talk/special sessions
on your related research areas.
Please make a large diffusion among interested colleagues and industrials.
Thank you in advance for your cooperation.


Organizing committee of MCO'08

